  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    AnalyticsCounter
    Reads the symptom data file, counts and sorts the data by key and value.
    CountAndSortSymptomDataFromFile
    Reads the file line by line, then uses the following filter. if the value of the row contains the "symptom" property of an element object in the list, then, we increment the value of its "occurrence" property otherwise, we create an object for the new symptom and initialize its occurrence value to 1 and insert it into the list
    ReadSymptomDataFromFile
    Simple brute force implementation
    WriteSymptomDataToFile
    Takes a Map as parameter, and write the values and keys of its elements, in the file.
